  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🦫 BEAVER RAMPAGE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the paws of a <strong>murderous beaver</strong> and unleash chaos wherever you go!<br><strong>BEAVER RAMPAGE</strong> is a wacky experience full of explosions, wood, and... hats.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🔥 What do you do?</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bite people (literally).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Munch down trees like a pro.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build wooden bridges with the logs you collect.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Destroy wooden buildings like there's no tomorrow.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shoot weapons and cause mayhem.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get caught in traps.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experiment, have fun, and wreck everything.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All of it wrapped up in a charming, low-poly world of pure destruction.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎩 Game Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Funny game with levels</strong> — each level is a new playground of chaos.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Constant updates</strong> — new levels will be added <strong>frequently</strong>!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Beaver customization</strong> — unlock and change hats to match your style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Low system requirements</strong> — runs smoothly even on older machines.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Growing gameplay time</strong> — more content with every update.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you've ever dreamed of being an angry beaver with a passion for wood and destruction — this is your moment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BEAVER RAMPAGE</strong> – <i>never underestimate a beaver with a gun.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >